  "texts": [
    "A detailed quantitative breakdown of how these metrics are computed can be found in the Methods section.",
    "In order to compare different models and optimize their performances, we first perform a grid search for hyperparameter optimization.",
    "For each model, we adjust three independent hyperparameters to assess the model's performance across different hyperparameter combinations.",
    "For a detailed breakdown of the chosen hyperparameters and their respective values, please refer to the Methods section.",
    "Here, we utilize the average value from six metrics to identify the optimal hyperparameter combination, given that all metrics are within the same range and scale."
  ]
}